title: For Sale:  9mm lee loader
postcontent: The 9mm Lee Loader kit sells for $28 new, when you can get them. I've reloaded about 40 rounds with this one before I realized that I really needed a full-blown press and dies for cast reloading. Lee should really let you know that a kit such as this one is really only good for reloading jacketed and perhaps plated bullets. To reload cast bullets, one needs to bell the case mouth and lightly crimp the final product. You cannot crimp with the lee loader. This kit is clean and comes with everything that was included. If after making your monthly NRA donation you have an extra $20, email me and we could meet in Waukesha or perhaps Madison.
